##API Security Testing Lab

Tools: Burp Suite, Postman, sqlmap
Activities: Tested DVWA API for OWASP API Top 10 vulnerabilities, exploited weaknesses, documented findings.

Vulnerability Log:

Test ID   Vulnerability	      Severity	       Endpoint
008	      BOLA	               Critical       	/api/users
009       	GraphQL Injection 	High	           /graphql

Manual Testing: Manipulated API tokens in Burp Suite to access unauthorized data.

